  "translations": {
    "en": "\"Indeed, they used to stand in prayer at night and not sleep, and they would fast during the day and not eat, and they would fight the enemy without cowardice, and they would give charity without stinginess.\"",
    "ur": "بے شک وہ رات کو قیام کرتے تھے ... صدقہ دیتے تھے اور بخل نہیں کرتے تھے۔",
    "tr": "\"Şüphesiz onlar geceyi ibadetle geçirirler ... cimrilik etmezlerdi.\"",
    "fa": "\"همانا آنان شب را به عبادت می‌ایستادند ... بخل نمی‌ورزیدند.\"",
    "id": "\"Sesungguhnya mereka dahulu bangun beribadah ... bersedekah tanpa pelit.\"",
    "bn": "\"নিশ্চয়ই তারা রাতে দাঁড়িয়ে ইবাদত করত ... কৃপণতা করত না।\"",
    "es": "\"Ciertamente, ellos solían orar de pie ... daban caridad sin tacanería.\"",
    "fr": "\"Certes, ils priaient debout la nuit ... donnaient en charité sans avarice.\"",
    "de": "\"Wahrlich, sie pflegten die Nacht im Gebet zu stehen ... Almosen zu geben ohne geizig zu sein.\"",
    "ru": "\"Воистину, они выстаивали ночь ... давали милостыню и не скупились.\"",
    "zh": "\"确实，他们曾在夜晚站立祈祷 ... 施舍而不吝啬。\""
  }
